892
01:06:56,730 --> 01:07:03,973
Total funding for this year has been about the same, a little bit different, with a larger shift in Title IV student support money.

893
01:07:04,893 --> 01:07:08,555
The federal government has readjusted funding levels and our state will receive less money.

894
01:07:09,355 --> 01:07:12,257
State receives less money, our district receives less money.

895
01:07:13,597 --> 01:07:14,778
