903
01:08:02,480 --> 01:08:09,841
What does it mean to add to something versus to shift the burden from the locality to the feds?

904
01:08:10,622 --> 01:08:13,222
That's something that comes up all the time.

905
01:08:14,722 --> 01:08:19,365
We're hopeful that, you know, we'll get clarity on this sooner rather than later so we can plan.

906
01:08:20,185 --> 01:08:25,448
