1049
01:17:28,996 --> 01:17:31,738
So a little bit of planning right now would be helpful.

1050
01:17:31,778 --> 01:17:33,219
We're going to wish it away.

1051
01:17:33,780 --> 01:17:34,660
Mr. Benedetto.

